Rating: 4
My sister had a brook trout and we were wondering what to do with it, so I pulled up this recipe from the site. It was delicious, and super easy! The flavors were perfect together. The ginger flavor is strong though, so you might want to tone that down if you don't prefer that flavor very much. I'd make it again with a nice, firm white fish like halibut or cod, would seem to lend itself better to this recipe - the flavors overpowered the trout. Excellent though, will make many times over!

